com.facebook.buck.core.rules.analysis.action

Interface ActionAnalysisDataKey


  • public interface ActionAnalysisDataKey
    The key used to look up the corresponding ActionAnalysisData.

    This key has the BuildTarget to look up the corresponding rule anlaysis computation that produced the desired ActionAnalysisData. The ActionAnalysisData.ID is the unique identifier of the desired ActionAnalysisData, which is used to identify the ActionAnalysisData of the many that a single rule analysis of a BuildTarget could produce.
